---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import sglTruckingVideo from "../assets/SGL-Trucking-LTD.mp4";
---

<Layout title="SGL Trucking">
  <!-- HERO -->
  <div class="text-white relative h-[100vh] w-full">
    <video
      autoplay
      muted
      loop
      aria-label="DashCam footage of a truckers journey."
      class="absolute top-0 object-fill h-[100vh] w-full"
    >
      <source src={sglTruckingVideo} type="video/mp4" />
    </video>
    <div
      class="absolute bottom-1/4 w-full flex justify-center flex-col text-center"
    >
      <h1 class="font-bold text-6xl">SGL TRUCKING LTD.</h1>
      <p class="text-xl font-light">
        LOGISTICS AND TRUCKING COMPANY IN SURREY / DELTA, BRITISH COLUMBIA
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <!-- HERO END -->

  <main class="h-auto text-stone-600 text-center">
    <div class="w-full bg-slate-100 pt-12">
      <div class="m-auto p-4 max-w-[calc(100% - 2rem)] max-w-[800px]">
        <h2 class="text-4xl text-stone-800">SGL Trucking Ltd.</h2>
        <h3 class="text-2xl text-stone-800">
          A trucking Company situated in Surrey / Delta B.C.
        </h3>
        <br />

        <p>
          SGL Trucking Ltd. is a Logistics and Trucking company based in Surrey
          / Delta B.C. Canada. It was established in 2010, since this time we
          have acquired experienced, professional employees/drivers who are
          constantly thriving for excellence. Their motivation has quickly
          turned this company into one of the largest transportation companies
          in The Greater Vancouver Region.

          <br />
          <br />

          SGL trucking Ltd. thrives on meeting our customersâ€™ needs. Our
          experience have allowed us to provide our customers with reliable and
          on time service. SGL Trucking Ltd. understands that the transportation
          industry is constantly advancing and in order to remain competitive
          and effective we are continuously expanding our services.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="w-full bg-stone-200 pt-12">
      <div class="m-auto p-4 max-w-[calc(100% - 2rem)] max-w-[800px]">
        <h3 class="text-4xl text-center text-stone-800">
          Why choose SGL Trucking LTD?
        </h3>
        <br />
        <p>
          SGL Trucking has emerged as a leading international trucking company
          in Canada and the United States of America. By blending the latest in
          trucking and transport technology with the traditional values of
          quality services, on-time delivery and responding to the needs of the
          customer, our company has become the service carrier of choice. After
          all those years of work and dedication SGL Trucking has made their
          name in the International market as the most reliable Trucking
          Company. SGL Trucking Ltd. is the reliable source for all your
          trucking and transportation needs. We can handle all kind of loads
          whether its a dry trailor, thin wall trailer, heated trailer or any
          size and weight. We can manage your load and can deliver it anywhere
          in US and Canada. We have our own Truck and Trailor insurance;
          therefore, we got you covered, you don't have to worry about the load.
          Your load is in safe and secure hands.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="w-full bg-stone-200 pt-12">
      <div class="m-auto p-4 max-w-[calc(100% - 2rem)] max-w-[800px]">
        <h3 class="text-4xl text-center text-stone-800">
          Freight all over the US and Canada.
        </h3>
        <br />
        <p>
          Our goal at SGL Trucking is to provide the highest level of
          transportation services as well as safe and timely deliveries, with
          fair and competitive pricing while providing a safe workplace for our
          employees and maintaining integrity, fairness and honesty with our
          customers and business partners.
        </p>
        <div class="w-full flex justify-center mt-4">
          <button
            class="bg-blue-600 text-base py-2 px-6 rounded text-slate-50 transition-colors hover:bg-blue-500"
            >Request a Quote</button
          >
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="w-full bg-stone-100 pt-12">
      <div class="m-auto p-4 max-w-[calc(100% - 2rem)] max-w-[800px]">
        <h3 class="text-4xl text-center text-stone-800">
          Environmental Policy
        </h3>
        <br />
        <p>
          SGL Trucking Ltd. operates a fleet of trucks and trailers, it is vital
          that we abide by a strict environmental policy which helps us avoid
          leaving a disastrous and costly negative environmental impact for
          future generations and wildlife.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col">
        <div
          class="text-left m-auto p-4 max-w-[calc(100% - 2rem)] flex flex-col sm:flex-row"
        >
          <div class="w-full sm:w-1/2 px-1.5">
            cool img here
            <h3 class="text-2xl text-center text-stone-800">
              Company Expectations
            </h3>
            <br />
            <p class="text-base">
              Employment of a truck and trailer maintenance program which
              ensures used parts, waste oil and any other by-products are
              disposed of and recycled in a responsible manner. Our trucks are
              outfitted with all EPA (Environment Protection Agency) emissions
              control equipment to reduce carbon footprint. Our fleet is
              maximally maintained to ensure efficient operation. Our drivers
              are actively trained to employ our environmental policies.
              Conservation, reduction, reusing and recylcing are used whenever
              possible along with our constant search of new technologies and
              innovative practices to limit waste and usage of resources.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="w-full sm:w-1/2 px-1.5">
            cool img here
            <h3 class="text-2xl text-center text-stone-800">
              Driver Expectations
            </h3>
            <br />
            <p class="text-base">
              Speeding is the number one source of poor fuel mileage and
              unnecessary carbon emissions that is within the driver's control.
              We encourage our drivers to drive at the posted speed limits. Our
              drivers are also directed to leave their trash in proper waste
              disposal containers and recycle bottles and other recyclables
              wherever possible while out on a trip.Speeding is the number one
              source of poor fuel mileage and unnecessary carbon emissions that
              is within the driver's control. We encourage our drivers to drive
              at the posted speed limits. Our drivers are also directed to leave
              their trash in proper waste disposal containers and recycle
              bottles and other recyclables wherever possible while out on a
              trip.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <button
            class="bg-orange-600 text-base py-2 px-6 rounded text-slate-50 transition-colors hover:bg-orange-500"
            >Read More
          </button>
        </div>
        <br />
        <br />
      </div>

      <div class="w-full bg-sky-600 pt-12 text-slate-50">
        <div class="m-auto p-4 max-w-[calc(100% - 2rem)] max-w-[800px]">
          <h3 class="text-3xl text-center">Are you looking for work?</h3>
          <h2 class="text-2xl text-center">We are hiring!</h2>
          <br />
          <p class="text-base">
            Do you have a Class 1 License with Air brake certificate?
            <br />
            Do you have relevant driving experience in US and Canada?
          </p>
          <div class="w-full flex justify-center mt-4">
            <button
              class="bg-orange-600 text-base py-2 px-6 rounded text-slate-50 transition-colors hover:bg-orange-500"
              >Apply Today</button
            >
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  main {
    font-size: 20px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  h1 {
    font-size: 4rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 1em;
  }
</style>
